layout: "main.njk"
pageTitle: "Performer Registration"
---
<h2>Performer Registration</h2>

<div id="performer-registration-app" class="performer-registration">
  <section id="performer-registration-start" class="performer-registration-panel">
    <p>
      If you would like to register interest in playing at a future sydney.emom, enter your email address below.
      We will send you a one-time link that lets you create or update your profile and select the event dates you are available for.
      Your profile goes live on the day of the first event you play, and (for now at least) it is free and in perpetuity.
    </p>
    <p>
      <b>NB: this system is under active development and may contain bugs.</b> If you encounter any issues please <a href="/contact">contact us.
      <b>NB # 2:</b> We are having some issues</b> with Apple email addresses (@icloud, @mac, @me) not receiving our emails and are working to rectify. Please use another account if possible, or <a href="/contact">contact us directly</a> thanks!
    </p>
    <form id="performer-registration-start-form">
      <label for="performer-registration-email">Email address</label>
      <input type="email" id="performer-registration-email" name="email" required>
      <button type="submit">Send registration link</button>
    </form>
  </section>

  <section id="performer-registration-session" class="performer-registration-panel" hidden>
    <p>How it works: about 10 days before each event, we email artists who have nominated that date to confirm availability. 
      From there, one week before the event we curate and invite a lineup for that night. If we have more performers than spots and you're not invited for that date, 
      your nomination gets 'standby' status in case someone can't make it and a spot opens up. To keep it fresh, we won't invite acts that have already played 
      at one of three previous events, but we give those 'backup' status, again in the event of not having enough acts to complete a lineup (usually 7-8 acts)</p>

    <form id="performer-registration-session-form">
      <label for="performer-email-display">Email address</label>
      <input type="email" id="performer-email-display" readonly>

      <label class="performer-registration-checkbox">
        <input type="checkbox" id="performer-is-email-public" name="is_email_public">
        <span>Show email on your profile page</span>
      </label>

      <label for="performer-profile-type">Profile type</label>
      <select id="performer-profile-type" name="profile_type" required>
        <option value="person">Person</option>
        <option value="group">Group</option>
      </select>

      <label for="performer-display-name">Display / stage name</label>
      <input type="text" id="performer-display-name" name="display_name" required>

      <label for="performer-first-name">First name</label>
      <input type="text" id="performer-first-name" name="first_name">

      <label for="performer-last-name">Last name</label>
      <input type="text" id="performer-last-name" name="last_name">

      <label class="performer-registration-checkbox">
        <input type="checkbox" id="performer-is-name-public" name="is_name_public">
        <span>Show full name on your profile page</span>
      </label>

      <label for="performer-contact-phone">Contact phone number</label>
      <input type="text" id="performer-contact-phone" name="contact_phone" required>
      <p class="performer-registration-note">Not displayed on your profile, only required in case we need to contact you urgently on the day of the event.</p>

      <label for="performer-artist-bio">Artist bio (visible on profile page)</label>
      <textarea id="performer-artist-bio" name="artist_bio" rows="6"></textarea>

      <label for="performer-additional-info">Additional info (not shown on profile)</label>
      <textarea id="performer-additional-info" name="additional_info" rows="4" placeholder="Put here anything else we might need to know, technical requirements, accessibility needs etc"></textarea>

      <fieldset class="performer-registration-fieldset">
        <legend>Social links</legend>
        <div id="performer-social-links"></div>
        <button type="button" id="performer-add-social-link">Add social link</button>
      </fieldset>

      <fieldset class="performer-registration-fieldset">
        <legend>Nominate the dates you're able to play</legend>
        <p id="performer-events-note" class="performer-registration-note"></p>
        <div id="performer-event-options"></div>
      </fieldset>

      <button type="submit">Submit for moderation</button>
    </form>
  </section>
</div>

<script src="/assets/scripts/performer_registration_form.js"></script>
